name: DroneFabio
description: Start an awesome app with AngularJS on the front, Socket.io + Express + Node on the back. This project is an application skeleton for writing [AngularJS](http://angularjs.org/) apps that use web sockets to add real-time functionality. If you're not planning on using web sockets, you should consider the [Angular Express Seed](https://github.com/btford/angular-express-seed) instead.
author: Fabio Duarte Euzebio
